text: Suvi Minkkinen (born 8 December 1994) is a Finnish biathlete. She made her World Cup debut in 2017 in Östersund, Sweden. At club level she represents Joutsan Pommi. In addition to biathlon she has also competed in cross-country skiing at national level. She participated in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:People from Joutsa Category:Finnish female biathletes Category:Olympic biathletes of Finland Category:Biathletes at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2015 Winter Universiade
